title: PM exchanges Eid greetings with Chairman Senate, NA Speaker
content:
LAHORE, Apr 22 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Saturday here telephoned Chairman Senate Sadiq Sanjrani and Speaker National Assembly Raja Pervaiz Ashraf and exchanged Eid greetings with them.The PM also made a telephone call to Deputy Speaker National Assembly Zahid Akram Durrani and greeted him on the auspicious occasion.Chairman Senate, Speaker National Assembly and Deputy Speaker thanked the prime minister and expressed their best wishes for him.
